text: Zeng Wanzhong () (1894 – 1968) was a KMT general from Yunnan. He was made a lieutenant general in April 1935. He commanded the 5th Army Group from February 1939 to March 1942. He fought against the Imperial Japanese Army in Shanxi. ==External Links== * Category:National Revolutionary Army generals from Yunnan Category:1894 births Category:1968 deaths
title: Zeng Wanzhong
